dct_title_s: Typus orarum maritimarum Guineæ, Manicongo Angôlæ ultra promontorium Bonæ spei usq
dct_alternative_sm: Marine map of Guinea, Manicongo and Angola to the Cape of Good Hope
dct_description_sm: Companion map to NOR 0239b, which form a map of Africa and the surrounding seas. This map is from the Dutch edition published in 1596. The sea contains two compass roses. Inset: Views of Ascension and St. Helena.
